column5: Got out oat Jordan Harbour for a few hours in the morning.  We Caught a couple of fish trolling.   We went 2/3 in 3 hours of fishing.  Water temp was 44 F.  Good to get the salmon skunk out of the boat.   The biggest was about 17.5.    We got this lamprey off of it and released her.
Some real nice looking fish you got there!
whadda know ! an actual fishing report  Great looking fish , don't target them myself but nice fish none the less.  Thanks for posting  TB
Nice fish Greg!  Now get back to the store!!!  lol
good job...i can wait to start hitting them.....in August...LOL...nicely done
Great report and pics greg  Man must of feel real good to land those bruts    Congratulations and thanks for sharing Leechman
